# Global rules

- Praxo-PICOS is a separate product repo from MemoryOS.
- Do not reuse MemoryOS ports, repo-root runtime paths, or launch scripts without intentional migration.
- Every code change must add or update tests unless docs-only.
- Every bug fix must include a regression test.
- Do not weaken privacy, localhost-only defaults, or secret handling.
- Use the smallest coherent change needed to satisfy the issue.
